        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No CRT for our Military Kids Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits funding for the Department of Defense Education Activity from being used to (1) teach critical race theory in any school operated by the activity, or (2) develop or distribute any curriculum that incorporates critical race theory.</p>]]>
        </text>
